mknutsen.graphicslibrary

Class GraphicObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • mknutsen.graphicslibrary.GraphicObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bullet, Button, Player

    public abstract class GraphicObject
extends java.lang.Object
    GraphicObject has all of the basic components for any rectangular based on object that will be being displayed including position, width, height, and velocity.
    Author:
    Max Knutsen - mknutse1@umbc.edu
